title.narrative: Global Health Professional and Organizational Development (GHPOD)
Professionnel de la santé global et développement organisationnel (GHPOD)

description.narrative: Le projet procurera également au bureau global de santé, aux bureaux régionaux, et aux missions de champ d'USAID d'accéder aux spécialistes indépendants, y compris ceux des universités, du non-pour-bénéfice, et des organismes de pour-bénéfice et d'obtenir des services techniques des experts principaux pour soutenir des secteurs d'intérêt stratégique à USAID.

The GHPOD program is focused on improving the effectiveness of USAIDs health sector by developing and increasing capacity of its health professionals through high quality professional and organizational development services worldwide. GHPOD provides a variety of PD and OD activities that focus on technical, management, leadership, and personal and effectiveness. The prime contractor is Social Impact with sub-contractors Deloitte and Management Systems International (MSI). GHPOD is a base-year plus two option years Task Order under the Transparency, Accountability, and Performance (TAP) Indefinite Quantity Contract (IQC).
